description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 Minute Guided Meditation | Clear & Calm The Mind In Uncertain Times' from the channel Boho Beautiful Yoga.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 15 minute guided meditation to clear and calm the mind is a perfect powerful practice for beginner & experienced meditation practices.  It is perfect tool to help cope with the uncertainty, to ground and rebalance yourself and your constant wandering mind. 

Through the simple act of reconnecting with your inner self and practicing the idea of positive affirmations of gratitude for the simple things in life, this easy guided meditation is perfect for anyone that is needing some positivity and calm during these uncertain times. It is time to let go of the negativity, stress, anxiety....whatever is holding you back in your life. Let this class take you on a meditative journey to cleanse and heal yourself from the inside out.

As you close your eyes and virtually join me on this meditative canoe ride through the Amazon River in Peru, may gift yourself the opportunity to let go of all that no longer serves you. Let go of the tension, the stress, the anxiety, the fear, whatever it is t...
